## ğŸ”’ Security & Privacy

- **ğŸ” Secure**: Never commit `.env` files to version control
- **ğŸ“ Read-only**: Package only reads your data, never modifies it
- **ğŸ  Local**: All analysis runs on your computer - no data transmitted
- **ğŸ”’ Encrypted**: Uses MongoDB Atlas encrypted connections

